longBusinessSummary: LAMF Global Ventures Corp. I does not have significant operations. It intends to effect a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. The company focuses to acquire opportunities in media, entertainment, and sports, as well as e-commerce and technology industries. LAMF Global Ventures Corp. I was incorporated in 2021 and is based in West Hollywood, California.
